snippet.title: Best VGM 2429 - Castlevania : Curse of Darkness - Eneomaos Machine Tower
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 03 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y5HHYuQi7cQ
Best VGM 22 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-BmGDtP2t7M
Best VGM 164 - http://youtube.com/watch?v=rVmt7axswLo
Best VGM 324 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rv7-G28CPFI
Best VGM 584 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5BZKMlqbPI
Best VGM 1195 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fJkpSSJUxC4
Best VGM 1974 - https://youtu.be/N2_yNExicyI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2 / Xbox
Castlevania: Curse of Darkness (2005)
Eneomaos Machine Tower
Michiru Yamane
